</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 space-bottom\" data-type=\"column\">\r\n\r\n<i class=\"mdi icon color1 mdi-fast-forward reverse round big\"></i>\r\n<h4 class=\"\">Mail Forwarding</h4>\r\n<p class=\"\">How to properly use and understand Ancillary Endorsements.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 space-bottom\" data-type=\"column\">\r\n\r\n<i class=\"mdi icon color1 mdi-dictionary reverse round big\"></i>\r\n<h4 class=\"\">Postal Dictionary</h4>\r\n<p class=\"\">Popular terms, acronyms and their definitions for direct mail.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 space-bottom\" data-type=\"column\">\r\n\r\n<i class=\"mdi icon color1 mdi-chart-donut-variant reverse round big\"></i>\r\n<h4 class=\"\">Mail Automation</h4>\r\n<p class=\"\">Mailing a letter at automation rates and using the USPS Notice 67.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-label=\"portfolio\" data-id=\"portfolio--1\" data-export-id=\"portfolio-2-materialis\" data-category=\"portfolio\" class=\"portfolio-2-materialis content-section-spacing-large content-section bg-color-white\" id=\"portfolio\" style=\"background-image: none; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<div class=\"gridContainer\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"section-title-col\" data-type=\"column\">\r\n<h2 class=\"\">Portfolio</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Check out a few of our projects which include postcards, envelopes, business cards and other direct mail marketing designs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 class=\"\"><a href=\"http://localhost/crst.net/portfolio\" target=\"_self\" class=\"\" data-cp-link=\"1\">View more Cornerstone Services direct mail designs</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row text-left spaced-cols center-sm\" data-type=\"row\" data-fixed=\"true\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12\">\r\n<div class=\"card mdc-elevation--z3 no-padding\" data-hover-fx=\"portfolio-1\">\r\n<div class=\"image\"><img src=\"http://loc